Traveling often means eating out a lot, and it’s so easy to lose track and overindulge. That’s why I like carrying a few wholesome snacks from home. Things like fruits, nuts, seeds, or something high in fiber help me feel satisfied and balanced before heading out for heavier meals. It’s a small habit that really helps me enjoy everything without going overboard.
